These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
Beverage: almond-milk, cola
Movie-Genre: disaster, epic
Sport: volleyball, basketball
Transport: motorbike, snowmobile
1. Transport:snowmobile is on the left or right of Sport:basketball##3
2. Beverage:cola is in an even position##4
3. Movie-Genre:epic == Beverage:almond-milk##1
4. Transport:snowmobile is on the right of Transport:motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | almond-milk  | cola   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic     | disaster   |
| Sport         | basketball | volleyball |
| Transport     | motorbike | snowmobile    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
Food: banana, raspberry
Movie-Genre: superhero, musical
Pet: hamster, pony
Transport: bike, helicopter
1. Pet:pony is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:superhero == Transport:helicopter##1
3. Food:raspberry is on the right of Movie-Genre:musical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | banana     | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | superhero  |
| Pet           | pony         | hamster     |
| Transport     | bike   | helicopter    |

